{"tid":1554763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(心理戰)大家改口叫警察,防暴同速龍做大陸曱甴,殺人犯,同老鼠,以其人之道還治其人之身","createTime":"2019-09-09T05:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T07:29:18.000Z","uid":272177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f653dac2d4a00abed1d51f44e2571a5ae331c046","tid":1554763,"uid":272177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"當我哋不斷俾班仆街叫做曱甴嘅時候，我哋一定唔好受！因為曱甴只為生存，心入面毫無價值觀可言，更加唔洗講有無良心。其實呢種物種就係同對面果啲武裝份子一樣，生存只為繁殖下一代，製造一代又一代嘅垃圾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家依家武裝份子入面絶對有理由相信有大陸解放軍喺入面！我哋要鬧黑社會嘅時候，一定要拖埋大陸班假警察落水！<br />\n所以見到以下情況，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得叫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警察=大陸曱甴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />防暴=殺人犯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />速龍=老鼠/過街老鼠</span></span><br />\n當然大家都相信入面全部都有大陸班仆街曱甴喺入面，其實隨時<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">叫佢哋任何一種廢柴做大陸曱甴</span></span>都得！<br />\n要等佢哋知道自己低下！犯濺！人見人憎！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以其人之道還治其人之身</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc65c4359846fc58514c0371443c9928a14a7d2","tid":1554763,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"【913 八月十五】 金鐘悼義士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554687</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XySvw4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXySvw4Z.jpg&h=8251e762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqGL5pZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqGL5pZ.jpg&h=af6e3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abab8a7f2b53fbf73f5688ea608ef8c31dd998cf","tid":1554763,"uid":283587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"我認同防暴真係要改名，因為自己友都叫佢地防暴，某程度上仲係認同佢地嘅工作<br />\n<br />\n所以要改名，幫佢地正名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b854d256014e27530dc55be668c95fd8fb26fd1","tid":1554763,"uid":40407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:25:09.000Z","msg":"其實冇唔好受，因為我唔係！<br />\n佢地俾人話狗唔好受，因為佢地都知自己係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb0b00ed99b518ef40563050f6d4898bb9e750a","tid":1554763,"uid":272177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abab8a7f2b53fbf73f5688ea608ef8c31dd998cf","tid":1554763,"uid":283587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"我認同防暴真係要改名，因為自己友都叫佢地防暴，某程度上仲係認同佢地嘅工作<br />\n<br />\n所以要改名，幫佢地正名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:06:39.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;認同&rdquo;呢個詞講得好啱！改佢哋名就係要將佢哋喺市民面前嘅樽鹽拎番落嚟！否定佢哋喺全部人心目中嘅認受性！"},{"pid":"f81b58455e185b86821ced3bd2bb6a3b9935c19f","tid":1554763,"uid":272177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b854d256014e27530dc55be668c95fd8fb26fd1","tid":1554763,"uid":40407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:25:09.000Z","msg":"其實冇唔好受，因為我唔係！<br />\n佢地俾人話狗唔好受，因為佢地都知自己係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:13:15.000Z","msg":"我哋要改佢名，就係要令到佢哋無晒威嚴！正如啲人見到速龍果陣大叫&ldquo;速龍呀！快啲走！&rdquo;，你諗班速龍聽到仲唔覺得自己好撚巴閉，心理上完全無怯咁去捉我哋！<br />\n再者，當有市民被落單，身傍啲人醒起佢係俾速龍捉住，啲人點敢救人？<br />\n但當大家話有人俾老鼠捉咗！我哋就會有個意識就係：&ldquo;仆街！打老鼠！&rdquo;<br />\n所以要改口呀！要滅佢哋士氣，先要滅佢哋威風！"},{"pid":"a462e1e73dbcd7dfca79a9d8c19e49bbf95eae82","tid":1554763,"uid":272177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"要滅狗嘅士氣，先要滅佢哋威風！<br />\n將班武裝份子嘅正名，全部變晒做我哋市民唔恐懼嘅名！仲要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有咁黑人憎得咁黑人憎！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ff3f02cb63c93921231dd11dfbd7f7bd1e0eafab","tid":1554763,"uid":272177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43e8d814075d7803856f7b3726dc194b092f5330","tid":1554763,"uid":272177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:52:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95ca629f2acf36a431a1ae524d9de2dff63cde4b","tid":1554763,"uid":272177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:26:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e92070760000da54c1315f04eb93f8295dafab4","tid":1554763,"uid":272177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"推"}]}